---
const quickLinks = [
    { text: 'Beranda', href: '/' },
    { text: 'Tentang SMSG', href: '/tentang' },
    { text: 'Visi & Misi', href: '/visi-misi' },
    { text: 'Program', href: '/program' },
    { text: 'Galeri', href: '/galeri' },
    { text: 'Kontak', href: '/kontak' }
];

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-primary-dark text-white">
    <div class="container-custom py-12 sm:py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            <!-- Organization Info -->
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <img src="/smsg-white-logo.png" alt="SMSG Logo" class="w-10 h-10" />
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-2xl">SMSG</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Wadah persatuan dan pengembangan mahasiswa UINSA yang berasal dari Trenggalek dalam membangun kontribusi nyata bagi masyarakat, daerah, dan bangsa.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick Links -->
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4 text-accent">Tautan Cepat</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                    {quickLinks.map((link) => (
                        <li>
                            <a href={link.href} class="nav-link text-white/80 hover:text-accent text-sm">
                                {link.text}
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    ))}
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Info -->
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4 text-accent">Hubungi Kami</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
